	<div id="himanshu-kathpal" class="speaker-bio">
		<div class="title-wrapper">
			<img alt="Himanshu Kathpal" class="headshot" height="65" src="https://q-website-images.s3.amazonaws.com/www/image/headshots/himanshu-kathpal.png" width="65">
			<div>
				<h2 class="title">Himanshu Kathpal</h2>
				<h3 class="job-title">Sr. Director, Product Management, Platform, Qulays</h3>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="bio">
			<p>Himanshu Kathpal is senior director of Product Management at Qualys. He has over 13 years of experience in cybersecurity and product management, with a specialization in vulnerability management, remediation, and next-generation endpoint security. Himanshu is passionate about developing security solutions that align with the company’s cybersecurity product strategy to meet customer needs, reduce the attack surface, and strengthen the organization’s security posture. He holds a master’s degree in engineering from D.Y.Patil University, Pune, as well as an MBA in International Business Management from NMIMS, Mumbai.</p>

